{"type":null,"faqId":14597,"title":"连接 WLAN 成功后经常自动断开，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">成功后，请保持在</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">热点的有效距离内，避免由于距离太远导致网络信号弱从而自动断开。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若在有效距离内仍然会出现自动断开的情况，可能是由于手机与提供热点的路由器不兼容。请重启</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">开关或重启路由器。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置界面，点击</span><span><img width=\"29\" height=\"21\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171708237001.gif\"> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">高级</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，然后点击<b>在休眠状态下保持</b></span><b><span> WLAN </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，打开选项菜单，选择<b>始终</b>。手机将始终保持与</span><span>\nWLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">网络的连接。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span><img width=\"557\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828171708385002.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":11,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6627","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1409217432000,"seriesProductName":"Holly-T00,Holly-U10","visitedTimes":601,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}